question: Hello my name is kacy, im currently 11 weeks postpartum. On my 37th week prenatal visit i developed protein in my urine and a slight case of preeclampsia. I delivered at 38 weeks 2 days and had no complications during labor. Now 11 weeks postpartum I have regular blood pressure but still  a lot of protein in my urine. I recently went to the doctors and now my ALT levels are high in my liver panel.All im wondering is if this is do to pregnancy or should I have some other concern>?
title: Postpartum Pregnancy Problems
